<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>os-oidc · OPNsense plugin feed</title>
<meta name="description" content="Signed pkg repository for the os-oidc OPNsense OpenID Connect login plugin.">
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#0b0f1a; --bg2:#111726; --card:#141b2d; --line:#243049;
    --ink:#e8edf7; --muted:#93a0bd; --accent:#5b8dff; --accent2:#7c5cff;
    --ok:#3fd08a; --code:#0c121f; --radius:16px;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  html,body{margin:0}
  body{
    font:16px/1.6 ui-sans-serif,system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Inter,sans-serif;
    color:var(--ink); background:
      radial-gradient(1100px 600px at 15% -10%,rgba(124,92,255,.18),transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(900px 500px at 100% 0%,rgba(91,141,255,.16),transparent 55%),
      var(--bg);
    min-height:100vh; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  .wrap{max-width:820px; margin:0 auto; padding:64px 22px 72px}
  .logo{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; margin-bottom:30px}
  .logo svg{width:46px; height:46px; flex:0 0 auto}
  .logo b{font-size:20px; letter-spacing:.3px}
  .logo span{color:var(--muted); font-size:13px; display:block; font-weight:400}
  h1{font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,46px); line-height:1.1; margin:.1em 0 .35em; letter-spacing:-.02em}
  h1 em{font-style:normal; background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));
    -webkit-background-clip:text; background-clip:text; color:transparent}
  .lede{color:var(--muted); font-size:18px; max-width:60ch; margin:0 0 26px}
  .badges{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-bottom:38px}
  .badge{display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; font-size:13px;
    padding:6px 12px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:999px;
    background:var(--bg2); color:var(--ink)}
  .badge .dot{width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--ok);
    box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(63,208,138,.14)}
  .badge code{color:var(--accent); font-size:12px}
  .card{background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--card),var(--bg2));
    border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:var(--radius); padding:26px 24px;
    margin:18px 0; box-shadow:0 18px 50px -28px rgba(0,0,0,.7)}
  .card h2{margin:0 0 4px; font-size:18px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px}
  .card h2 .n{width:26px; height:26px; flex:0 0 auto; border-radius:8px;
    display:grid; place-items:center; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2))}
  .card p{color:var(--muted); margin:.3em 0 1em; font-size:14.5px}
  pre{position:relative; margin:0; background:var(--code); border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:12px; padding:16px 46px 16px 16px; overflow-x:auto}
  code,pre,kbd{font-family:ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace}
  pre code{font-size:13.5px; color:#cdd9f5; white-space:pre}
  pre code .c{color:#6b7a9c}            /* comment   */
  pre code .k{color:var(--accent)}      /* command   */
  pre code .s{color:var(--ok)}          /* string/url*/
  .copy{position:absolute; top:9px; right:9px; border:1px solid var(--line);
    background:var(--bg2); color:var(--muted); font-size:11px; padding:5px 9px;
    border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; transition:.15s}
  .copy:hover{color:var(--ink); border-color:var(--accent)}
  .copy.done{color:var(--ok); border-color:var(--ok)}
  .grid{display:grid; gap:14px; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  @media(max-width:620px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .links{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; margin-top:34px}
  .links a{display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; text-decoration:none;
    color:var(--ink); border:1px solid var(--line); background:var(--bg2);
    padding:10px 15px; border-radius:11px; font-size:14px; transition:.15s}
  .links a:hover{border-color:var(--accent); transform:translateY(-1px)}
  .fp{font-size:12px; color:var(--muted); word-break:break-all}
  .fp code{color:var(--accent)}
  footer{margin-top:46px; color:var(--muted); font-size:13px; border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    padding-top:20px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px}
  footer a{color:var(--accent); text-decoration:none}
  a{color:var(--accent)}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <div class="logo">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
      <defs><linearGradient id="g" x1="0" y1="0" x2="48" y2="48">
        <stop offset="0" stop-color="#5b8dff"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#7c5cff"/>
      </linearGradient></defs>
      <rect x="9" y="21" width="30" height="20" rx="5" fill="url(#g)"/>
      <path d="M15 21v-5a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v5" stroke="url(#g)" stroke-width="3.4"
        stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/>
      <circle cx="24" cy="30" r="3.2" fill="#0b0f1a"/>
      <rect x="22.7" y="31.5" width="2.6" height="6" rx="1.3" fill="#0b0f1a"/>
    </svg>
    <div><b>os-oidc</b><span>OPNsense · OpenID Connect login</span></div>
  </div>

  <h1>The signed <em>pkg feed</em> for os-oidc.</h1>
  <p class="lede">A hardened OpenID Connect authentication plugin for OPNsense,
     delivered as an RSA-signed package repository. Pin the key once — every
     install and upgrade is cryptographically verified.</p>

  <div class="badges">
    <span class="badge"><span class="dot"></span>RSA-signed catalogue</span>
    <span class="badge">latest&nbsp;<code>@VERSION@</code></span>
    <span class="badge">ABI&nbsp;<code>@ABI@</code></span>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2><span class="n">1</span>Trust the feed</h2>
    <p>Pin the repository config and its signing key on the firewall (run as root).</p>
    <pre><button class="copy">copy</button><code><span class="c"># repo config + signing public key</span>
<span class="k">fetch</span> -o /usr/local/etc/pkg/repos/oidc.conf <span class="s">@PAGES_URL@/oidc.conf</span>
<span class="k">fetch</span> -o /usr/local/etc/pkg/keys/oidc.pub  <span class="s">@PAGES_URL@/pkg-repo.pub</span></code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2><span class="n">2</span>Install the plugin</h2>
    <p>Refresh the catalogue and install. Upgrades later are just <code>pkg upgrade</code>.</p>
    <pre><button class="copy">copy</button><code><span class="k">pkg</span> update <span class="c"># verifies the signature against oidc.pub</span>
<span class="k">pkg</span> install os-oidc</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h2 style="font-size:16px">Managed fleets</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:0">Pinned across nodes with Ansible via the
        <code>opnsense_oidc_repo</code> role — no manual fetch needed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2 style="font-size:16px">Signing key</h2>
      <p class="fp" style="margin-bottom:0">SHA-256 of <code>oidc.pub</code>:<br>
        <code>@KEY_SHA256@</code></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="links">
    <a href="@REPO_URL@">↗ Source &amp; docs</a>
    <a href="@REPO_URL@/releases/latest">⬇ Releases</a>
    <a href="@PAGES_URL@/oidc.conf">oidc.conf</a>
    <a href="@PAGES_URL@/pkg-repo.pub">pkg-repo.pub</a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <span>Built &amp; signed by CI on every <code>v*</code> tag.</span>
    <span><a href="@REPO_URL@">@REPO_SLUG@</a></span>
  </footer>

</div>
<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.copy').forEach(function(b){
    b.addEventListener('click',function(){
      var t=b.parentElement.querySelector('code').innerText;
      navigator.clipboard.writeText(t).then(function(){
        b.textContent='copied'; b.classList.add('done');
        setTimeout(function(){b.textContent='copy'; b.classList.remove('done');},1400);
      });
    });
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
